<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Harmony Haven!</title>
    <style>
        /* Responsive CSS */
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                width: 100% !important;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f0f0f0;">
<table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center" width="600" class="container" style="margin: auto;">
    <!-- Header -->
    <tr>
        <td bgcolor="#ffffff" style="padding: 20px 0; text-align: center;">
            <img src="https://projemya.com/harmonyhaven/harmony_haven_logo.png" alt="Harmony Haven Logo" width="200">
            <h1 style="margin: 20px 0;">Welcome to Harmony Haven, ${name}!</h1>
            <p style="margin: 0;">We're thrilled to have you on board.</p>
        </td>
    </tr>
    <!-- Content -->
    <tr>
        <td bgcolor="#ffffff" style="padding: 20px;">
            <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">Here's what we've got for you:</h2>
            <ul style="list-style-type: none; padding: 0;">
                <li><strong>Daily Motivation:</strong> Get inspired with our daily dose of motivating articles and quotes.</li>
                <li><strong>Personal Growth:</strong> Explore tools and resources to help you grow and thrive.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Thanks for joining Harmony Haven! Dive in now and start your journey.</p>
            <p>Got questions or feedback? We're here for you!</p>
            <p><strong>Best regards,</strong><br>The Harmony Haven Team</p>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
